Elegance in Every Stroke Madhubani Swan

Presenting my Day 29 entry for the #MadhubaniWithMegnificArt challenge by @megnificart a graceful Swan in Mithilas intricate Kachani. In Indian symbolism, the swan or Hamsa represents purity, wisdom, and spiritual evolution. Through delicate linework and vibrant hues, this artwork reflects the soulful calm and serenity swans are known for.

Original artwork created with love and rooted in tradition.

Follow @sonatamink for more folk art! DM for prints and commissions.

Madhubani Swan Painting, Mithila Art, Indian Folk Art, Hand-drawn Swan, Swan Motif in Madhubani, Traditional Indian Painting, Folk Art Symbolism, Bharni Kachani Swan, Purity in Art, Artistic Indian Culture
